name: palm oil, refined, to generic market for vegetable oil, refined | vegetable oil, refined | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/3071/documentation

Vegetable oils are often traded on the same market, simply because most of the uses requiring vegetable oil do not require a specific vegetable oil. The purpose of this activity is to link certain amount of a specific vegetable oils and create generic vegetable oil which can be then traded on generic vegetable oil market.

This activity renames part of the refined palm oil to "vegetable oil, refined" for sale on this more generic vegetable oil market.
